    "game-id": "65867188454ad97feb216bac5a257c6a",
    "spell_type": "focus",
    "rank": 4,
    "text": "You take on the stance of the flowing winds, sending out waves of energy at a distance. You can make wind crash unarmed Strikes as ranged Strikes against targets within 30 feet. These deal 1d6 bludgeoning damage; are in the brawling group; and have the agile, nonlethal, propulsive, and unarmed traits. Wind crash Strikes ignore concealment and all cover.  \n  \n While in wild winds stance, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against ranged attacks.",
